Paper: hep-th/9401001

Date: 1994-01-03

Title: Remarks on the Collective Quantization of the SU(2) Skyrme Model

Authors: Jorge Ananias Neto

Comments: 8 pages, plain tex, IF/UFRJ/94

Journal-ref: J.Phys. G21 (1995) 695-700

We point out the question of ordering momentum operator in the canonical\break quantization of the SU(2) Skyrme Model. Thus, we suggest a newdefinition for the momentum operator that may solve the infrared problem thatappears when we try to minimize the Quantum Hamiltonian.